name: Listen Tee [Mens]
description:
Hey you, yeah you, "Listen" up!

Michigan Made Music presents "Listen," the first album from the MMM group featuring 30 Michigan artists on 17 amazing tracks. Now we are offering these super soft tee's to commemorate the album. Get em' while you can and support the mitten!

BELLA + CANVAS Triblend Short Sleeve Tee
Printed graphic on front, inside tag, and back
Model is 6' 2" and wearing a Large

Grey Triblend jersey fit
50% polyester / 25% combed & ring-spun cotton / 25% rayon
